00:31:41.332 --> 00:31:44.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but when I get nervous, I fart.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:31:44.135 --> 00:31:46.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You… are you…</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:31:47.605 --> 00:31:48.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>doing this on purpose?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:31:51.943 --> 00:31:56.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-No, you're wrong--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You traitor, prepare yourself!</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:32:01.886 --> 00:32:03.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:32:04.389 --> 00:32:07.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's this, you're a farter too…</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:32:07.926 --> 00:32:12.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh! It's not just a fart,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there's liquid coming out.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:32:12.096 --> 00:32:14.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He's probably got </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>korori</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What?</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:32:14.966 --> 00:32:16.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's terrible.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:32:17.235 --> 00:32:18.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pull yourself together!</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:32:19.237 --> 00:32:21.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A man stained with barbarian stench.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:32:21.539 --> 00:32:24.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being saved by an illness</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that foreigners brought here, how funny.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:32:25.410 --> 00:32:26.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isn't it, Tachibana?</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:32:29.480 --> 00:32:30.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Indeed…</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:32:34.852 --> 00:32:37.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, is there a good doctor around here?</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:32:38.957 --> 00:32:40.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's just a sick man right now.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:32:47.765 --> 00:32:50.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a tenement in Honjo Aioi-cho,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there was a doctor named Minakata.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:32:51.769 --> 00:32:53.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems he is treating </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>korori</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:32:53.271 --> 00:32:56.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Dr. Minakata is there?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Do you know him?</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:32:57.408 --> 00:32:58.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know who you are,</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:33:00.578 --> 00:33:01.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I owe you.</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:33:09.721 --> 00:33:12.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, what did you need from me?</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:33:15.693 --> 00:33:19.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This kind of medicine doesn't work!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>My diarrhea won't stop.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:33:19.697 --> 00:33:22.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand it's tough,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it will get better gradually.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:33:26.137 --> 00:33:29.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What a mess.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Hey, hurry up and clean it up.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:33:29.540 --> 00:33:31.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please wait a moment!</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:33:59.537 --> 00:34:01.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kiichi, are you okay?</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:34:04.709 --> 00:34:06.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just threw up a lot…</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:34:10.548 --> 00:34:11.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My hand.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:34:13.017 --> 00:34:14.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Looks like grandpa's hand.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:34:16.287 --> 00:34:19.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The water inside the body is coming out.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:34:20.558 --> 00:34:21.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why…</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:34:23.094 --> 00:34:24.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to drink this, right?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:34:38.876 --> 00:34:41.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I die here.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:34:42.780 --> 00:34:45.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor, you'll have to do without…</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:34:46.884 --> 00:34:47.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Huh?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:34:49.821 --> 00:34:53.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The beans for my mom's surgery.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:34:54.258 --> 00:34:56.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I said I'd give you beans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the rest of my life.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:34:59.630 --> 00:35:01.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I counted them.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:35:03.401 --> 00:35:07.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Beans costs five </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>mon </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>for one bunch, right?</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:35:07.705 --> 00:35:10.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought your reward</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would be about two </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ryo</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> in total.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:35:12.276 --> 00:35:18.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Gen, the vegetable vendor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who is good at bookkeeping taught me.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:35:20.384 --> 00:35:23.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If five bunches are delivered every day</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:35:25.890 --> 00:35:29.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd have to deliver beans for 520 days.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:35:30.294 --> 00:35:31.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And these beans</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:35:33.064 --> 00:35:38.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>can only be harvested</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for about two months a year, so</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:35:38.903 --> 00:35:43.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd have to stay alive until I'm about 20.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:35:43.107 --> 00:35:46.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor, you'll be losing the payment.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:35:50.148 --> 00:35:51.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right, Kiichi.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:35:52.183 --> 00:35:53.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So do your best!</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:35:59.891 --> 00:36:00.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kiichi!</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:36:09.467 --> 00:36:11.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Isn't it strange how things change, Miki?</i></c.bg_transparent>

466
00:36:16.174 --> 00:36:21.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Until this morning,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>I wished not to change anyone's fate.</i></c.bg_transparent>

467
00:36:28.886 --> 00:36:33.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Right now, I want to somehow</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>change this child's fate.</i></c.bg_transparent>

468
00:36:38.462 --> 00:36:41.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That wasn't good…</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:36:48.873 --> 00:36:51.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Jin!</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:36:54.879 --> 00:36:56.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>How long has it been, I wonder.</i></c.bg_transparent>

471
00:36:57.648 --> 00:36:59.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>To care about someone this much.</i></c.bg_transparent>

472
00:37:00.585 --> 00:37:01.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Save someone.</i></c.bg_transparent>

473
00:37:02.787 --> 00:37:06.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>To genuinely want to save them</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>from the bottom of my heart.</i></c.bg_transparent>

474
00:37:11.796 --> 00:37:12.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kiichi, listen.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:37:14.065 --> 00:37:15.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>God…</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:37:16.434 --> 00:37:18.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>sends only trials that we can overcome.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:37:23.407 --> 00:37:24.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So let's work hard together.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:37:36.554 --> 00:37:37.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Minakata!</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:37:52.903 --> 00:37:53.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saki.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:37:53.904 --> 00:37:56.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor, I believe there are limits</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to what you can achieve alone.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:37:57.408 --> 00:38:00.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For the sake of the patients,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I thought it was better that way.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:38:01.579 --> 00:38:03.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Maybe this is unnecessary, but--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:38:05.049 --> 00:38:06.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you very much.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:38:19.263 --> 00:38:22.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Ogata, I have a favor to ask…</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:38:22.199 --> 00:38:28.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>First, could you tell me about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the treatment method for </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>korori</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>?</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:38:30.141 --> 00:38:32.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll listen to your favor after that.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:38:36.514 --> 00:38:41.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Korori</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> is an infectious disease caused</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by a germ we call the cholera bacterium.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:38:42.386 --> 00:38:43.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please move!</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:38:44.021 --> 00:38:46.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Patients quickly get dehydrated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and collapse.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:38:46.724 --> 00:38:50.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's hard to muster any strength,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the skin loses its elasticity,</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:38:50.428 --> 00:38:52.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the eyes become sunken,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the cheeks hollow.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:38:53.264 --> 00:38:56.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The pulse becomes weak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and eventually leads to death.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:38:57.034 --> 00:38:58.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So what's the remedy?</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:38:59.003 --> 00:39:01.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because it's caused by losing water,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we need to replenish that.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:39:02.773 --> 00:39:04.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Make them drink water?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:39:04.975 --> 00:39:07.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Water, you say?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What nonsense!</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:39:07.144 --> 00:39:08.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I said water, but not just any water.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:39:09.380 --> 00:39:11.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>An oral rehydration solution</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with added salt and sugar.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:39:11.916 --> 00:39:13.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's called "ORS."</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:39:14.218 --> 00:39:15.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ORS?</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:39:15.720 --> 00:39:18.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is water that is in a state</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>close to the water in our bodies.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:39:19.623 --> 00:39:21.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a result, the water</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>becomes easier to absorb.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:39:22.460 --> 00:39:25.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need to keep giving this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the patient persistently.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:39:27.164 --> 00:39:29.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is that it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's all we can do for now.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:39:29.900 --> 00:39:32.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, is it possible to</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>kill the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>korori</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> bacteria?</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:39:32.770 --> 00:39:34.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unfortunately, it cannot be killed.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:39:35.172 --> 00:39:36.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But by doing this,</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:39:37.007 --> 00:39:40.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you can survive until the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>korori</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>bacteria are naturally expelled.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:39:40.978 --> 00:39:42.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then that means they aren't cured!</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:39:42.580 --> 00:39:45.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>korori</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> would't be cured</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by something like this.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:39:45.216 --> 00:39:47.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to Most,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we must administer opium or quinine,</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:39:48.018 --> 00:39:51.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>rub the patient's skin</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or bathe them to induce sweating.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:39:51.422 --> 00:39:54.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It takes a lot of effort</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to treat this illness.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:39:54.725 --> 00:39:56.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is also written in this manual.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:39:56.660 --> 00:39:58.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think that treatment is effective.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:40:01.532 --> 00:40:02.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How dare you!</c.bg_transparent>

